{"tid":692603,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有無人記得Britain's Got Talent(2007)嘅Connie Talbot?","createTime":"2018-06-06T21:54:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T02:29:42.000Z","uid":82747,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"597394968997d41322ae4702bf36e2a44adedeb4","tid":692603,"uid":82747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T21:54:19.000Z","msg":"個陣年紀只有六歲嘅佢 參加左Britain's Got Talent 雖然輸左 但係憑住佢動人嘅歌聲同可愛嘅外貌 都入到總決賽 而且比冠軍更加耀眼<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/07/054928_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F07%2F054928_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=0995ab66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/07/051652_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F07%2F051652_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=af4f374e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n參選歌曲為&quot;Over The Rainbow&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n比賽完左之後 佢就即刻同左一間唱片公司簽約 亦發佈左第一張嘅專輯 雖然得到好多負面嘅評價 但係喺全球銷售左二十五萬張 而且喺三個國家同地區嘅銷量都排名第一<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/07/055248_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F07%2F055248_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=47ce348a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後一直都喺台同電視上表演 到左佢十四,十五歲個陣 佢已經學識彈琴 仍然有喺YouTube配合琴聲翻唱其他歌 同發行自己嘅歌 佢嘅外貌依然幼氣 但係更加多嘅係仙氣<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/07/052553_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F07%2F052553_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f014f444&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/07/052600_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F07%2F052600_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=1a19d200&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/07/054553_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F07%2F054553_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=84d87276&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/07/054736_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F07%2F054736_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=842357c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n慢慢到左大個 都依然好鍾意唱歌 繼續出歌翻唱 但係唱嘅類型就同佢個樣一樣 成熟左好多<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/07/054401_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F07%2F054401_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=08e52965&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/07/054405_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F07%2F054405_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1e596763&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/07/054830_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F07%2F054830_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=c2c7457f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由細睇住佢大 真係好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實有無人發現啲達人show <br />\n總有一個細路係會入到決賽"},{"pid":"ffbf31d855a17bea9eeb43f23defb484fc339ac1","tid":692603,"uid":82747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T07:38:01.000Z","msg":"真係無人識咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e18d7b6d7079042cffcd0ef5ef59e0380c644b6","tid":692603,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T15:46:15.000Z","msg":"有, count to me好正"},{"pid":"e8153b09c5a467a89d4434a23eb6c5ccf81d7c0b","tid":692603,"uid":82747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e18d7b6d7079042cffcd0ef5ef59e0380c644b6","tid":692603,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T15:46:15.000Z","msg":"有, count to me好正"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:22:10.000Z","msg":"count on me<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢live唱呢首同播緊CD無分別"},{"pid":"94a7415a481636e44cea99249748604c15ea4b30","tid":692603,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T02:24:01.000Z","msg":"愈大愈唔同，希望佢唔好行錯路，將來做巨星"},{"pid":"3c09a1c523e7e2548d272c4222378a64c749b046","tid":692603,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T02:29:42.000Z","msg":"好靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}